<br>
It's much better to just go there and if someone is there, go somewhere else.  It's not as if you wasted time -- you get xp on your travel down to wherever it was you wanted to go and redirecting is pretty easy.<br>
<br>
'Course there are those that just go there and setup camp where you are without even saying hello, too.  Had that happen the other night in Kedge.  I had the whole second level cleared and a group came down, setup in the other cubby next to me, and started pulling without even saying hello.  Kinda rude.<br>
<br>
Wasn't much of a problem.  They looked pretty clumsy.  So, I passed on a group offer (after I said hello and inquired about their intents) and moved on to the shark pool -- less xp for more work, but at least they wouldn't be able to kill me.  Glad I did that; 20 minutes later I hear a ton of shouting and then they're gone.  When I check the second level again, they're all dead and they've got 4 impalers camping them.  How they managed to wipe when they had an enchanter along and where they managed to even get 4 impalers from an area that was completely cleared and spaced puzzles me to this day.<br>
<br>
Ah well, I'm just glad I was only doing xp and not camping a named or I'd have been more inclined to ask them to move on instead and that would have been unpleasant.  So back to the shout topic; the only shout that really has much meaning is about train-related issues.  They're big, they're red, and they're rude, but when you have something of potentially large importance to say, that's just what you want.  Uh, that's important to your audience, not important to you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ulunnaao.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lunna AO</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Evil Kitten From Hell</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/26/02 1:22:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2790.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.anarchylore.com/GFILES/UserPic51285_8164.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Eh, I mostly ignore &quot;camp check&quot; shouts ..</span><hr size=1> Wtf use new technology ffs you noob!<br>
