<br>
Also, if I'm at a camp and I hear you, I'm probably not going to respond, anyway. If I'm in the middle of a battle, most shouts scroll by unread and uncared about.  If I don't see the word train, I don't even look at it, and these days, I ignore the train shouts unless they actually give a location, since shouts are zone wide.<br>
